metadata.title: 18th National Assembly session commences under Speaker Ayaz Sadiqâ€™s chairmanship

content.article_body: ISLAMABAD, Aug 04 (APP): The 18th session of the National Assembly commenced on Monday under the chairmanship of Speaker Sardar Ayaz Sadiq at the Parliament House. The session began at 5:10 PM and is expected to take up various legislative and non-legislative agenda items, including bills, resolutions, and matters of public importance.
